    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The procedure involves multiple steps, including transaction management, conditional logic, and logging. It handles potential errors using a TRY-CATCH block and updates multiple tables, which adds to its complexity."
        }
